---
title: Sweet-Soy & Sticky Plum Chicken with Golden Roast Veggies & Creamy Slaw
description: Sometimes it’s too hard to wait for something sweet, so we’ve come up with a plan. Satisfy those cravings with a
plum sauce to make a sticky coating for seared chicken. A creamy slaw will help to elevate things, not to mention
the roasted veggies. Enjoy pleasing your tastebuds!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
